name: The Mod’s Twin Daughters
description: Twin daughters of The Moderator. Permabanned from entering the Powermod house because they accidentally saw their father’s DM once and that they got into NFT. Cursed with double facepalm of you shall not see no more, they wandering the dark land searching for the truth and justice, somehow along the way developed the ability to listen to the constellation that guided them to who knows where. Wielding a cute labrys and a fancy sword stolen from their father’s head, they do some fight against the evil forces once in a while, not every time, because not much enemy in this land, and abundant of frens <3
